---
import { COUNTRY, COUNTRY_FLAG } from '../../lib/constants'
import Card from '../Card.astro'
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Hi, I'm Dwi, a frontend software developer from {COUNTRY}
      {COUNTRY_FLAG}.
      <br />
      <br />
      My primary tools of choice includes:
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc">
        <li>JavaScript</li>
        <li>Next.js</li>
        <li>React</li>
        <li>TypeScript</li>
        <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
        <li>Prisma</li>
        <li>Nodejs</li>
        <li>Astro</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      I usually learn coding by watching some tutorial videos on YouTube.<br
      /><br /> Besides coding, I usually watch anime, read manga or novels, play
      games, or browse social media.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
